ime":"2020-02-22T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"有無睇過modern love? 我個人覺得幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f074bf291071788ecf566a5794f2064175f2b07","tid":1892692,"uid":42229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"好煩 同屋企太耐 同屋企人都多左好多爭拗"},{"pid":"249f5b91fff1fde90d0bcade5f0e4b59bcad7f46","tid":1892692,"uid":240224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f643ae961d5f3fce5c343cc0aff3eb9502bdfca","tid":1892692,"uid":292497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"操fit自己準備抗爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"係屋企得閒就郁下做下運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b287a4238dc39204b6fdd52b0827096b7199abe7","tid":1892692,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a852f28cd4a380a58e212d03925717788a0bf92a","tid":1892692,"uid":57308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8a40f8f327fa422e2a198650c34116de05b5af9","tid":1892692,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"睇書，打機"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"睇左美劇兩日，個人開始有啲躁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"我都睇緊，不過係紙牌屋"},{"pid":"84b229d2dbb553888b4851bbd849d7f71fcbb603","tid":1892692,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"打機 睇劇 睇小說"},{"pid":"6e695ff138a30ba58ac774077d03e79fcd895e1a","tid":1892692,"uid":182222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"由於以前職業原因 我成日都留喺屋企 可以俾D建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 操fit 自己<br />\n一定要做運動，尤其是依家武肺，建議買D resistance bands 每日花一個鐘頭操，網上我見$500有齊唔同磅數阻力夠做<br />\n<br />\n2. 想打發時間既可以煲劇<br />\n但係我個人唔建議，因為我覺得時間唔係咁浪費的，一日睇唔好睇太耐，1-2集已經係極限，我睇過覺得唔錯既劇有：<br />\n美劇 Good doctors, Breaking Bad<br />\n台劇：惡作劇之吻，我可能不會愛你，必娶女人<br />\n英劇：Skin, Inside No.9 (9號秘事）<br />\n韓劇：Pinocchio, Doctor異鄉人<br />\n<br />\n3. 讀書<br />\n屌你趁依家有時間讀多D書啦後生仔，歷史、經濟、政治、小說類總有一款啱，想由入門學起既話建議地Khan Academy, 上網睇多D人地書籍推介，等圖書館開翻落去借<br />\n<br />\n4. 學樂器<br />\n呢個唔洗點解釋啦，不過冇興趣唔洗勉強<br />\n<br />\n5. 有D人會試下做blogger/ youtuber<br />\n呢個係我朋友親身經驗，佢有D學識，上網寫一D關於政治博弈、時事評論既文章，可能你地都有睇過、不過唔開名啦，個人認為可以試下自己有興趣既嘢擺上網，反正你都冇嘢做"},{"pid":"e1b8b0ef5e6e1376f90bded5ed8c646dea6a0eb0","tid":1892692,"uid":88725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"阿媽痴線<br />\n我都痴左線<br />\n今晚終於打爆左部電視<br />\n我覺得自己有精神病"},{"pid":"e46306fb764b4e523f988c6f29e5393fd05001f2","tid":1892692,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15e2b82694ab1303e7b0a3f8451569bcf2985bca","tid":1892692,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e46306fb764b4e523f988c6f29e5393fd05001f2","tid":1892692,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1b8b0ef5e6e1376f90bded5ed8c646dea6a0eb0","tid":1892692,"uid":88725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"阿媽痴線<br />\n我都痴左線<br />\n今晚終於打爆左部電視<br />\n我覺得自己有精神病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"有乜咁好笑？<br />\n我阿媽腸癌<br />\n我細佬條女唔聽人講仲去飲<br />\n我細佬今晚仲去酒店陪佢訓<br />\n之後攪到我阿媽發癲<br />\n因為怕肺炎"},{"pid":"34e0671d15d9051140823af9617b8acfbfa41878","tid":1892692,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"日日屌藍絲老豆老母"},{"pid":"af1bcc3f0f7fb3be04b1544ca4dfcd9e7c9b638c","tid":1892692,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f074bf291071788ecf566a5794f2064175f2b07","tid":1892692,"uid":42229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"好煩 同屋企太耐 同屋企人都多左好多爭拗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:02:38.000Z","msg":"屋企細<br />\n我都係"},{"pid":"cf9f3a68aec3afad362f7595d0a03bc8a77ba598","tid":1892692,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s